:"https://vip.opstream11.com/share/a0def054ef84ac2784ea52baee05d95f","link_m3u8":"https://vip.opstream11.com/20220620/31836_9930e34b/index.m3u8"},{"name":"40A","slug":"40a","filename":"thanh-thanh-tu-kham-qing-qing-zi-jin-tap-40A","link_embed":"https://vip.opstream11.com/share/27230ac1c8d9d2828e1ff531bec85d37","link_m3u8":"https://vip.opstream11.com/20220620/31834_d6fa0fab/index.m3u8"},{"name":"40B","slug":"40b","filename":"thanh-thanh-tu-kham-qing-qing-zi-jin-tap-40B","link_embed":"https://vip.opstream11.com/share/aebb462e657b9e288cbfe408fc1a9dd5","link_m3u8":"https://vip.opstream11.com/20220620/31837_ae07dea7/index.m3u8"}]}],"time":"45 phút/tập","description":"<p>\"Thanh Thanh Tử Khâm\" thuộc thể loại học đường cổ trang, được chuyển thể từ tiểu thuyết \"Cung Học Hữu Phỉ\" của tác giả Ngô Ngọc. Bộ phim xoay quanh câu chuyện về Lạc Thu Trì, một chàng thư sinh quyết tâm trở thành một nhà thơ vĩ đại. Anh thi vào Học Viện Trúc Tụ - nơi nuôi dưỡng, đào tạo tài năng thi nhân trẻ, gặp gỡ những anh tài khác và cả ý chung nhân đời mình. Tại nơi này, Lạc Thu Trì và hội bạn cùng nhau trải qua những khó khăn, vui có buồn có, cùng nhau trưởng thành, và rồi một câu chuyện tình lãng mạn nảy nở.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"107656","season":1,"vote_average":7.2,"vote_count":6},"modified":"2022-07-12T06:57:27.000Z","cast":["Fan Shiqi","Lv Xiaoyu","Tạ Bân Bân","Yan Yiyi","Huang Xuan Wen","Yu Ting'er","Hua Tong","Trương Thần Quang","Trương Vũ Kỳ"],"director":["Xu Fei"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Fan Shiqi","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Fan Shiqi","tmdb_id":1683308,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/imfIKp7uOsHz2LzZD97yj2LwBRn.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1683308"},{"name":"Lv Xiaoyu","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Lv Xiaoyu","tmdb_id":2343728,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bLBJkHqqRAPPrjbjzhNzrj4nkhq.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://